Titolo: Ballance (video game)

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: Ballance is a 3D puzzle video game for Microsoft Windows. It was developed by German studio Cyparade, published by Atari Europe and first released in Europe on 2 April 2004. The gameplay is similar to Marble Madness: the player controls a ball via mouse and keyboard, moving it along a course while trying not to fall off the screen. The game is now considered abandonware, and neither the developers nor publishers are actively tracking its copyrights.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
